<li>
<p>
Is this system consistent?  If so, why?  If not, why not?
<md>
  <mrow> x_1 -2x_2 + x_3 \amp \mathstrut =  0 </mrow>
  <mrow> 2x_2 - 8x_3 \amp \mathstrut =  8 </mrow>
  <mrow> -4x_1 + 5x_2 + 9x_3 \amp \mathstrut = -9 </mrow>
</md>
This system can be reduced to the triangular form: 
<md>
  <mrow> x_1 -2x_2 + x_3 \amp \mathstrut =  0 </mrow>
  <mrow> x_2 - 4x_3 \amp \mathstrut = 4 </mrow>
  <mrow> x_3 \amp \mathstrut =  3 </mrow>
</md>
It can be written in augmented matrix form as 
