  <mrow> 5x*1 -7x_2 + 9x_3 \amp \mathstrut =  0 </mrow>
</md> 
The augmented matrix for this system can be row reduced to produce <me>\begin{bmatrix}0 \amp 3 \amp -6 \amp 8 \\ 1 \amp -2 \amp 3 \amp -1 \\ 5 \amp -7 \amp 9 \amp 0 \end{bmatrix} \sim \begin{bmatrix}1 \amp -2 \amp 3 \amp -1 \\ 0 \amp 3 \amp -6 \amp 8 \\ 0 \amp 3 \amp -6 \amp 5 \end{bmatrix} \sim \begin{bmatrix}1 \amp -2 \amp 3 \amp -1 \\ 0 \amp 3 \amp -6 \amp 8 \\ 0 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp -3 \end{bmatrix} </me>
</p>
