  <p>
    The equation <m>A{\mathbf{x}}={\mathbf{b}}</m> has a solution if and only if <m>{\mathbf{b}}</m> is a <fillin characters="10" />  <fillin characters="10" /> of the columns of <m>A</m>.
  </p>
</li>

