    <me> \begin{bmatrix} A \amp I \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} 2 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 1 \amp 0 \amp 0 \\ -3 \amp 0 \amp 1 \amp 0 \amp 1 \amp 0 \\ 0 \amp 1 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 1 \end{bmatrix} \sim \dots \sim \begin{bmatrix} 1 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp \frac{1}{2} \amp 0 \amp 0 \\ 0 \amp 1 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 0 \amp 1 \\ 0 \amp 0 \amp 1 \amp \frac{1}{2} \amp 1 \amp 0 \end{bmatrix} </me>
